data.meta_description: Celebrate Kansas with the Kansas State Fair Sept. 6-15, 2024! The Kansas State Fair has been the state's largest gathering of Kansans since 1913. The Fair  celebrates agriculture, provides entertainment, commercial exhibits, a world-class midway and much more.  Find tickets for our concerts.
